Sentencas: The advancement of symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells (SSOFCs) is hindered by the significant challenge of finding electrode materials that exhibit both high activity and superior stability.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, Ca-doped Pr0.5Ba05FeO3-delta (Pr0.5Ba01Ca04FeO3-delta, Ca-PBF) is investigated as an electrode material for SSOFCs.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The catalytic activity for oxygen reduction and fuel oxidation is greatly enhanced by the introduction of Ca into the Ba-site, leading to improved efficiency in oxygen diffusion.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C in air, the cathode polarization resistance decreases from 0.95 to 0.53 Omega cm(2) and the anode polarization resistance decreases from 2.42 to 1.23 Omega cm(2) when exposed to wet H-2.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With enhanced catalytic activity, the symmetrical cell with Ca-PBF exhibits a peak power density of 480 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C in wet H-2.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: More importantly, the symmetrical cell with Ca-PBF demonstrates stable performance for 100 h in wet H-2.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that Ca-PBF has great potential as an electrode material for SSOFC and can be one of the candidates for practical applications.
Titulo: Tuning Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ cathode to enhanced stability and activity via Ca-doping for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells
